&lt;li&gt;Expertise in HubSpot and Salesforce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage deep knowledge of HubSpot and Salesforce to drive efficiency and effectiveness in revenue operations.&lt;/li&gt;
